    "name": "Alaura",
    "profile": "Alaura O'Dell (formerly [a479849]) is the ex-wife of the artist now named [a=Genesis Breyer P-Orridge] and long-time [a=Psychic TV] collaborator, known also as [a=Mistress Mix]. \r\nShe is the mother of [a=Genesse P-Orridge] and [a=Caresse P-Orridge]. She and Gen split in 1992 and her work with PTV ended at the same time. She released a solo ambient music and spoken word album, [r=265279], in 1995. \r\n\r\nAlaura also runs the Sacred Journeys organization, offering women opportunities to travel to sacred places or power centers around the world.\r\n",
